---
title: "Tools — VibeWarden Ecosystem"
description: "Open-source developer tools from the VibeWarden ecosystem. HTTP debugging, traffic inspection, and more."
canonical: "https://vibewarden.dev/tools/"
navActiveId: tools
hasMobileNav: true
ogType: website
ogTitle: "Tools — VibeWarden Ecosystem"
ogDescription: "Open-source developer tools from the VibeWarden ecosystem."
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}


{% block pageStyles %}
<style>
    .tools-hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
    }

    .tools-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .tools-hero p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .tools-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .tool-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .tool-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--brand-purple);
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
    }

    .tool-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .tool-card h2 a {
      color: var(--text-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .tool-card h2 a:hover {
      color: var(--brand-purple);
    }

    .tool-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .tool-desc {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .tool-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tool-links a {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--brand-purple);
    }

    .tool-links a:hover {
      color: var(--brand-purple-light);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .tools-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .tools-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <div class="container">
      <section class="tools-hero">
        <h1><span class="gradient-text">Developer tools</span></h1>
        <p>Open-source utilities from the VibeWarden ecosystem. Each is a standalone tool — use them with or without VibeWarden.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="tools-grid">
        <article class="tool-card">
          <h2><a href="https://github.com/vibewarden/httptape">httptape</a></h2>
          <p class="tool-desc">Record and replay HTTP traffic. Capture requests and responses as tape files for debugging, testing, and building mocks. Lightweight CLI with zero dependencies.</p>
          <div class="tool-links">
            <a href="/docs/httptape/">Documentation</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/vibewarden/httptape">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="tool-card">
          <h2><a href="https://github.com/vibewarden/snitchproxy">snitchproxy</a></h2>
          <p class="tool-desc">Transparent HTTP proxy that logs every outbound request your app makes. Catch unexpected API calls, data exfiltration, and SSRF attempts during development.</p>
          <div class="tool-links">
            <a href="/docs/snitchproxy/">Documentation</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/vibewarden/snitchproxy">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
